pantheon-meteo (1.0.0-1) bullseye; urgency=medium

  * added provider selection from the list
  * added animation of the data request
  * add several hotkeys (ctrl+q, ctrl+p)
  * switching to the GPL3 license
  * improved the selection of units
  * added the ability to select the number of displayed days
  * added ScrolledWindow for forecast view that the window was not stretched
  * replaced the Wingpanel.Separator with Gtk.Separator
  * update names of libwingpanel dependency
  * updated app icon

